Package: egvtools
Title: High‑resolution Ecogeographical Variables Toolkit
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Andris", "Avotiņš", , "andris.avotins@lu.lv", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Helpers for reproducible geospatial workflows to create
    harmonised ecogeographical variables: terra/sf/sfarrow IO, tiling,
    extraction and zonal statistics, and gap‑filling utilities.
